    "note-2:note_value": "Date supplied taken from inclusive dates of Nom Preservation Foundation collection: 1667-1957",
    "note-3:note_value": "\"Thơ chữ Hán của nhiều người, lấy tên phần đầu theo tên tập của Vũ Văn Phụng. Tờ 1-8: Thơ Vũ Văn Phụng: Hoành Bồ huyện dõan đại đình Nguyễn danh ký thi [横䈬縣尹大庭阮名寄詩], Thu vịnh (4 bài) [秋詠], Hoà Ngô phu tử nguyên vận (2 bài) [ 和吾夫子元韻]. Tờ 12: Hương Khê huyện doãn Nguyễn Văn Mỹ ký thi [香溪縣尹阮文美寄詩]. Tờ 15-16: Phó ngự y Vân Canh tú tài Nguyễn Địch thi tập [副御醫云耕秀才阮迪詩集], có các bài: Trung nguyên dạ ức Hà Thành thân nhân [中元夜憶河城親因], Tảo thu bệnh trung tác [早秋病中作], Bát nguyệt ức Tây Hồ thắng du [八月憶西湖勝遊], Tự trào [自嘲], Thân diệc sơ [親亦疎]. Tờ 17: Diên Hưng tú tài Nhữ Liên hạ tân ốc thi [延興秀才汝連賀新屋詩] .\" (Thọ, p. 56).",
