    "note-1:note_value": "Classical Chinese",
    "note-2:note_value": "\"Các bài sớ cúng Phật vào các dịp lễ, giỗ chạp, con cúng cha mẹ, cha mẹ cúng con, chồng cúng vợ, vợ cúng chồng v.v…: Tiến tôn sư trai tuần cúng phật sớ 薦尊師齋旬供佛疏, Hạ nhật tiến tôn sư cúng Phật sớ 夏日薦尊師供佛疏, Huý nhật tiến phụ mẫu sớ 諱日薦父母疏, Phụ mẫu tiến nam tử các tiết sớ 父母薦南子各節疏, Thê tiến phu nhất thất trai tuần sớ 妻薦夫一七齋旬疏,… Tất cả 75 bài.\" (Thọ, p. 81).",
