    "note-1:note_value": "Classical Chinese and Vietnamese; (Nôm script)",
    "note-2:note_value": "Date supplied taken from inclusive dates of Nom Preservation Foundation collection: 1667-1957",
    "note-3:note_value": "\"Sách y dược, kê tên các cây thuốc: đại phong tử, thủ nhân thủy ngân, phòng phong đinh hương, lan mạt tử…Từng nhóm cây có ghi công dụng chữa bệnh gì, như: Trị phong thống chứng [治風痛症]- Nhĩ tập chứng [耳襲症]- Mục thống chứng [目痛症]- Khẩu bệnh chứng [口病症]- Thũng thống [腫痛]- Xỉ thống chứng [齒痛症]- Thổ huyết chứng [土眓症]- Thoát giang chứng [捝扛症]- Kinh quý chứng [驚季症]- Lâm bế chứng[淋閉症]- Hoa Đà chân nhân thương mạch luận [華陀真人滄脉論]: nói về các mạch độc...Các phương thuốc trị bệnh phụ nữ. Cuối sách chép mấy bài phú, văn tế: Tiền Xích Bích phú (Nôm), Tống bần tế văn (Nôm) [宋貧祭文], Tế tử bái khấn trướng văn [祭子拜懇悵文], Môn sinh khấp mẫu sư trướng văn [[門生泣母師悵文], Chinh Tây tướng sĩ tế văn [征西將士祭文].\" (Thọ, p. 139).",
