    "note-2:note_value": "Date supplied taken from inclusive dates of Nom Preservation Foundation collection: 1667-1957",
    "note-3:note_value": "\"Tập sách chép tay tác phẩm của Nguyễn Trãi. Nội dung gồm 2 phần: Phần 1: Dư địa chí 輿地志. Phần 2: Ức Trai thi tập 抑齋詩集, thơ chữ Hán, có các bài: Đề Hoàng ngự sử Mai Tuyết hiên 題黄御史梅雪軒, Côn Sơn ca 崑山歌, Đề kiếm 題劎, Hạ quy Lam Sơn 賀歸藍山, Thượng nguyên hỗ giá chu trung tác 上元扈駕舟中作. Sách biên chép cẩn than, nhưng do chép để dung, không một câu chữ nào cho biết tên người và năm tháng sưu tập, sao chép.\" (Thọ, p. 172).",
