    "note-1:note_type": "language",
    "note-1:note_value": "Classical Chinese",
    "note-2:note_value": "Trùng bản: R.702, R.3365, R.3305, R.3301, R.703",
    "note-3:note_value": "\"Bộ luật đầu tiên của triều Nguyễn ban hành dưới triều Gia Long vào năm 1813, cũng còn được gọi là luật Gia Long, toàn bộ gồm 22 quyển bao gồm cả dân luật và hình luật: q.1: Luật mục 律目 (hình vẽ về hình cụ, chế độ trang phục, giải thích thuật ngữ hình luật); q.2-3: Danh lệ 名例 (Ngũ hình 五刑, Thập ác 十惡, Bát nghị 八議, Ứng nghị giả phạm tội 應議者犯罪,…); q.4-5: Lại luật 吏律 (Chức chế 職制, Công thức 公式); q.6-8: Hộ luật 戶律 (Hộ dịch 戶役, Điền trạch 田宅, hôn nhân 婚姻,Thương khố 倉庫,…); q.9: Lễ luật 禮律 (Tế tự 祭祀, nghi chế 儀制); q.10-11: Binh luật 兵律 (Cung vệ 宫衛, quân chính 軍政,…); q.12-20: Hình luật 刑律 (Tặc đạo 賊盗, nhân mạng 人命, phạm gian 犯姦, tạp phạm 雜犯, đoạn ngục 斷獄,…); q.21: Công luật 工律 (Doanh tạo 營造, hà phòng 河防); q.22: Sách dẫn.\" (Thọ, p. 177).",
    "note-4:note_value": "Condition: Tốt/ Good ; q.02 : Tốt/ Good ; q.03 : Tốt/ Good ; q.04 : Tốt/ Good ; q.05: Tốt/ Good ; q.06: Tốt/ Good ; q.07: Tốt/ Good ; q.08: Tốt/ Good ; q.09: Tốt/ Good ; q.10: Tốt/ Good ; q.11: Tốt/ Good ; q.12: Tốt/ Good ; q.13: Tốt/ Good ; q.14: Tốt/ Good ; q.15: Tốt/ Good ; q.16: Tốt/ Good ; q.17 : Tốt/ Good ; q.18: Tốt/ Good ; q.19: Tốt/ Good ; q.20: Tốt/ Good",
