    "note-1:note_value": "Classical Chinese",
    "note-2:note_value": "Date supplied taken from inclusive dates of Nom Preservation Foundation collection: 1667-1957",
    "note-3:note_value": "\"Chép lại bộ sách cùng tên của Trung Quốc. Đầu sách có bài Tựa của Hòe Hiên nói về sự cần thiết phải nghiên cứu học tập thi luật, nói việc giải thích thơ chia làm các loại: Giải thích ý nghĩa, giải thích pháp mạch, giải thích về thể cách, qua nhiều cách giải thích như vậy kết cấu thơ được sáng tỏ.Cuối bài ký tên Tạ Tuân hiệu Mi Sĩ thị soạn tháng 8 năm Ung Chính 12. Tiếp theo là các bài, mục: Luận bằng trắc, luận vận, luận tuyệt cú…Cuối bài ký tên Hòe Hiên chủ nhân thư. Tờ 10 là bài: Hòe Hiên gia Thang Hải Nhược tiên sinh danh gia thi tuyển Thượng quyển…Đây là bản chép lại nguyên thư của Trung Quốc về đề tài Thi pháp học, rất cần thiết cho các nhà Nho nước ta, đương thời cũng như hiện nay thường là loại sách rất hiếm.\" (Thọ, p. 183).",
