    "note-2:note_value": "Date supplied taken from inclusive dates of Nom Preservation Foundation collection: 1667-1957",
    "note-3:note_value": "\"Nội dung: Mở đầu là bài Tiếng gà. Sau mới đến phần tên sách và nội dung chính. A. Sau phần tên sách có tiểu truyện về Lê Trãi 黎廌 tức Nguyễn Trãi 阮廌 từ lúc đỗ đạt làm quan đến khi về ở ẩn. Có kèm theo các chức tước, mỹ tự ông được ban tặng và liệt kê một số trước tác chính của ông: Ức Trai thi tập 抑齋詩集, Quân trung từ mệnh 軍中詞命…B. Trình quốc công Nguyễn Bạch Vân am tiên sinh thi tập 程國公阮白雲庵先生詩集 (thơ Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm)... cuối sách có bài La Sơn thập vịnh. Sau cùng có 1 trang ghi tên, hiệu, ngày tháng năm sinh của một số người, phần này có vẻ không liên quan gì đến nội dung chính của sách.\" (Thọ, pp. 425-426).",
