    "extent-1:extent_value": "1 online resource (10 volumes: q.01: 76 pages ; q.03: 77 pages ; q.04: 66 pages ; q.05: 67 pages ; q.06: 49 pages ; q.07: 44 pages ; q.08: 50 pages ; q.09: 66 pages ; q.10-11: 57 pages ; q.16-17: 120 pages)",
