    "note-3:note_value": "\"Mối mọt nhiều chỗ. Nội dung: 1. Diễn giải sách Đại học: Kinh văn 1 chương, truyện văn 10 chương (Tăng Tử tác), Thảo cú (Chu Tử tác). 2. Diễn giải sách Tử truyện về các chương: Thánh ý, Chính tâm tu thân, Tề gia trị quốc, Trị quốc bình thiên hạ. 3. Diễn giải sách Trung dung... Trung dung đồ thuyết: vẽ và giải thích các chi của thuyết Trung dung, Trung dung ca (chữ Nôm), Trung dung ba mươi ba chương, mỗi chương đều có diễn giải bằng quốc âm (chữ Nôm).\" (Thọ, pp. 106-107).",
