    "note-1:note_type": "language",
    "note-1:note_value": "Classical Chinese",
    "note-2:note_value": "Date supplied taken from inclusive dates of Nom Preservation Foundation collection: 1667-1957",
    "note-3:note_value": "Sách mất trang bìa, toàn bộ nội dung được chép bằng chữ Hán, phân chia làm nhiều mục khác nhau: Luận về ngũ khí, Luận về các mạch, Thuận về trường sinh trong ngũ hành, Phép nghịch trong ngũ hành, Tứ khôn, Bát tướng, Tam giác kì, Tứ thế cao, Nhật nguyệt minh; Luận về cát hung trong Sa pháp…",
