    "note-2:note_value": "Date supplied taken from inclusive dates of Nom Preservation Foundation collection: 1667-1957",
    "note-3:note_value": "\"Bài tựa nói thơ là thể hiện ý chí, chí khác nhau nên thơ viết ra cũng khác nhau. Bài tựa do Nguyễn Án, người Cối Kê, tỉnh Bắc Giang viết năm Bính Thìn. Sách gồm 2 tập thơ: Đông Dã học ngôn 東野學言 gồm các bài: Tặng lân y Lê ông [贈鄰醫黎翁], Quý cố viên hương [貴故園鄉], Trùng đăng Hàm Long tự chung các [重登咸鍾閣], Du Phúc Khánh tự [遊福慶寺], Ngọc trì tức sự[玉池即事], Nguyệt dạ văn địch [月夜聞笛 ], Tương Giang nguyệt [相江月], Vô đề [無題]…Phạm Quý Thích thi tập [范貴適詩集]: tập thơ gồm 10 bài như: Chu trung tức sự [舟中即事], Tống đồng niên Nguyễn Nhuận phủ chi Yên Kinh[送同年阮潤府之焉京], Thùy khởi ngẫu thành[垂起偶成], Bất vũ hứng [不雨興], v.v.\" (Thọ, pp. 134-135).",
